{"tid":1202660,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大家一齊些牙下文宣谷巴絲打嘅一番心血啦","createTime":"2019-06-11T09:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T17:26:27.000Z","uid":143347,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8f7ab6b9535a2c04aac525b8d759f5546f4ab9f3","tid":1202660,"uid":143347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:58:55.000Z","msg":"Hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地文宣谷巴絲打整左一大堆611 612嘅宣傳圖比大家，但好似仲未好廣泛流出，快啲一齊黎轟炸出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呼籲身邊嘅人，無論係咩派都好，繼續黎關心逃犯條例嘅情況啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（文宣谷有大量重覆嘅改ver圖，所以目測差唔多就無save低，可能放漏咗某啲巴絲打心血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />麻煩幫手post返上黎）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chitVOz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FchitVOz.png&h=ffdedf6e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T6aTntA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT6aTntA.png&h=4dde201a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bZ4wTAf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbZ4wTAf.png&h=d9e17454&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c1Od6Vg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc1Od6Vg.png&h=1e018c84&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PcsqX1W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPcsqX1W.png&h=1c03f70e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mLAHfOB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmLAHfOB.png&h=451415a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cBRjh1X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcBRjh1X.png&h=1acc409d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pJHqX1X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpJHqX1X.png&h=59174